出<br />\n<br />\n咁咪更加令香港人覺得更有需要行出嚟，連出街唔舒服帶個罩都會俾人拉，咁咪真正知道冇自由係點"},{"pid":"e6bb088e5a1d279d5e1c20017cf5f15a679a308d","tid":1617510,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:23:10.000Z","msg":"余錦賢：《緊急法》止暴成疑反成建制洩壓閥- <a href=\"http://信報網站hkej.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BF%A1%E5%A0%B1%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99hkej.com&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=59b2de98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">信報網站hkej.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2267708/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Farticle%2Fid%2F2267708%2F&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=f293135f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/article/id/2267708/</a>"},{"pid":"5c5f6fb9daeef7448bcb087e76383caf8b099cd2","tid":1617510,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:24:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"698c6b4af1d4164e298063d26b0ee289a4b61690","tid":1617510,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:27:12.000Z","msg":"建制狗仲未走出同溫層"},{"pid":"24ac1651d031a082982d709bd90113b30ef2a6d9","tid":1617510,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:28:47.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"6c1a1d8488d39dd5c0753b0c620d1020988f7288","tid":1617510,"uid":268090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"用火水救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6d65e1515876b6d5fb35106eec797008b511e3","tid":1617510,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T23:44:21.000Z","msg":"為左選票可以幾人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afff27fabef41ffd925ceae826986ad99e8ff995","tid":1617510,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci